---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = "June 7, 2025";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for calpercentage.com. We don't collect personal data. All calculations run in your browser. No cookies, no tracking."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-16 sm:py-24">

    <p class="form-label mb-4">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4" style="letter-spacing:-0.05em; line-height:1.1;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-line); padding-top:3rem;" class="space-y-10">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6">
          calpercentage.com is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect (very little), how we use it, and your rights. The short version: we don't collect personal data, we don't use tracking cookies, and all calculations run entirely in your browser.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Information we do not collect</h2>
        <ul class="text-sm text-secondary leading-7 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>No names, email addresses, or account information (there are no accounts).</li>
          <li>No calculation inputs — every calculation runs in your browser and is never sent to our servers.</li>
          <li>No payment data — the site is free with no purchases.</li>
          <li>No location data beyond what is standard in web server logs (see below).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Information we may collect automatically</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6 mb-3">
          Like most websites, our hosting infrastructure may log standard technical information when you visit, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-secondary leading-7 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Your IP address (anonymized or aggregated)</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
          <li>Referring URL</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6 mt-3">
          This data is used only for diagnosing technical issues and understanding aggregate traffic patterns. It is never sold or shared with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6">
          We use a single cookie-equivalent: a <code class="text-xs font-mono bg-canvas-soft-2 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">localStorage</code> entry called <code class="text-xs font-mono bg-canvas-soft-2 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">theme</code> to remember your dark/light mode preference. This value never leaves your device. We do not use advertising cookies, analytics cookies, or any third-party tracking cookies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Third-party services</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6">
          We use Google Fonts to load the Inter and JetBrains Mono typefaces. When your browser requests these fonts, Google may log the request per their own privacy policy. No other third-party services, analytics platforms, or ad networks are embedded on this site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Children's privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6">
          calpercentage.com does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13. The site is a free utility tool with no registration or user-generated content.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated "last updated" date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3" style="letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-6 mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please reach out via our contact page.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact us</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
